      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle is offered in pristine, showroom-grade condition, reflecting a legacy of meticulous preservation and exacting care. Every facet of this motorcar\u2014from its flawless exterior finish to its immaculate interior\u2014exudes the refinement expected of a premier luxury asset. We invite the discerning buyer to experience a vehicle that transcends the standard market offering, representing a rare opportunity to acquire a masterpiece of engineering in its most optimal state.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
