    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a standard that exceeds showroom expectations. The exterior features the original, deep-gloss factory finish, protected by a professional ceramic coating with zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show absolutely no bolster wear, and every electronic component functions with factory-new precision. Mechanically, it is flawless\u2014always garaged, never driven in inclement weather, and accompanied by a meticulous binder of every service record since the date of purchase. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year for a discerning collector who demands perfection. It drives as tightly as the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
