    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following the maintenance schedule. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a new home, this is the one! It drives like a dream and still has that fresh car smell. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
