      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is an exceptional E46 M3, a benchmark of naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, recently serviced with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rod bearing replacement using ARP hardware. The longitudinal chassis is structurally pristine, having undergone preventative subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, providing unparalleled mechanical grip and feedback. Every bushing and suspension component remains in factory-spec or better condition, preserving the communicative steering rack and neutral handling balance that defines this chassis. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example with documented maintenance history and zero deferred mechanical needs.",
